data.description: Welcome to your dream home, where elegance meets comfort, and convenience blends with luxury. This beautiful 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom residence is a true gem, offering a spacious and inviting living space designed for modern living. Situated in a prime location, this home is the epitome of gracious living, with each room thoughtfully crafted for your comfort and enjoyment. As you step inside, you are welcomed by a captivating entry foyer that exudes warmth and charm. This inviting entryway sets the tone for the entire home, making every guest feel right at home from the moment they arrive. The heart of the home is the living room, which boasts an abundance of natural light and offers a cozy space for relaxation and entertainment. The adjacent dining room is a spacious and elegant area where you can gather with family and friends for delicious meals and special celebrations. The den, complete with a charming fireplace, is the ideal spot for cozy evenings in front of a crackling fire. The large kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring a center island with seating and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. Cooking and entertaining are a breeze in this space, and the nearby pantry ensures that you have ample storage for all your culinary needs. For added convenience, you'll find a dedicated laundry room with a sink and cabinetry. The primary bedroom is a serene retreat, featuring a spacious walk-in closet. The en-suite bathroom is equipped with a jetted soaking tub and a beautiful tile shower, providing you with a spa-like experience within the comfort of your own home. The attention to detail is evident throughout the home, with crown molding and wainscoting that add an extra layer of elegance and sophistication, making it truly stand out. On the outside, you'll discover a covered front porch and covered rear deck, an ideal space for outdoor dining, entertaining, or simply enjoying the fresh air. With these outdoor features, you can make the most of every season. This property sits on a generous 1.05-acre lot, offering plenty of space to enjoy the great outdoors. The rear yard is fenced, providing privacy. There's also a bonus room for additional flexibility, and a large two-car attached garage for your vehicles and storage. In summary, this home is the epitome of luxury and comfort. It offers a gracious living space, a fantastic location, and a range of features that cater to modern living. The attention to detail and thoughtful design make this home truly exceptional. With its spacious rooms, luxurious primary suite, and beautiful outdoor spaces, this property is the perfect place to call home. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours and experience the best in modern living!
